      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal equivalency assessment between validation and COU input parameters is not required provided qualitative justification is provided.",
      "rationale": "The validation geometry (FDA generic pump) and the device under assessment share impeller diameter within 8%, similar blade count, and overlapping operating flow ranges. Qualitative equivalency is sufficient at MRL 2; formal parameter equivalency mapping was not performed."
    }
